Class SBSIFormatRegexps4

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.ed.csbe.sbsivisual.sbsiDataFormat.SBSIFormatRegexps4

public class SBSIFormatRegexps4
extends java.lang.Object

Patterns for SBSI parser validation for version 4 of SBSI data format. These are public for use by tool developers wishing to generate SBSI Data standard files

Author:
Richard Adams
